 inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">This leather belt from Valeo provides great support by stabilizing your spine during heavy lifts, thus, also preventing injuries. The belt also has double loops for extra safety.</p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Comfort</span>&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">One of the key highlights of this belt is its suede lining. It covers the inbuilt foam lumbar pad, thus providing excellent comfort during strenuous workouts. The padding also helps with the contraction and compression against your mid-section while you lift.&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Most of all, it fits comfortably as you can also adjust it according to your waist size, and it prevents discomfort while lifting. The only issue is with the holes and the buckle of the belt, as they appear to be a little fragile.</p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Material and Stitching</span>&nbsp;</p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">The belt has been made from 4-inch wide cowhide leather, which is why it is so sturdy. Its double-stitched edges not only provide safety but also comfort when you carry heavy loads.</p><p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Montserrat, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: inherit!important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"